#: ../../source/api/Strategies.rst:12
msgid "BaseStrategy"
msgstr "BaseStrategy"

#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy:1
msgid "基类：:py:class:`object`"
msgstr "基类：:py:class:`object`"

#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy:1
msgid "量化投资策略的抽象基类，所有具体策略都应从本类继承并实现交易信号生成逻辑。"
msgstr ""
"Abstract base class for quantitative strategies; concrete strategies inherit"
" from it and implement signal generation logic."

#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy:3
msgid ""
"一个完整的策略通常由三部分组成：可调参数（pars）、所需历史数据的声明 （data_types + window_length "
"等）以及基于这些数据生成信号的 ``realize()`` 逻辑。 在策略运行过程中，可通过 ``get_pars()`` 和 "
"``get_data()`` 访问参数与数据，输出 的实数信号再由 Operator 按 PT/PS/VS 信号语义解析为实际交易指令。关于自定义策略 "
"实现步骤与 PT/PS/VS 的详细说明，见文档「交易策略与 BaseStrategy」相关章节。"
msgstr ""
"A complete strategy usually has three parts: tunable parameters (``pars``), "
"declared historical data (``data_types``, ``window_length``, etc.), and "
"``realize()`` logic that turns data into signals. During runs, use "
"``get_pars()`` and ``get_data()``; the Operator parses numeric signals as "
"PT/PS/VS trade instructions. See the “Trading Strategies and BaseStrategy” "
"docs for custom strategies and PT/PS/VS details."

#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy:10
msgid "示例"
msgstr "Example"

#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy:11
msgid "BaseStrategy 为抽象基类，通常通过继承实现自定义策略。下面示例展示其类型信息（稳定输出）："
msgstr ""
"``BaseStrategy`` is abstract; implement custom strategies by subclassing. "
"The example below shows stable type output:"

