#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy.info:5
msgid "是否打印策略的运行状态"
msgstr "Whether to print strategy run state"

#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy.info:7
msgid "策略的ID，如果为None，则打印策略的名称，否则打印策略的ID"
msgstr "Strategy ID; if None, print the strategy name instead"

#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy.info:9
msgid "额外的信息，可以是任何字符串，会被打印在策略主信息之后，参数和数据之前"
msgstr "Extra text printed after main info and before parameters and data"

#: ../../source/api/Strategies.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr "Return type"

#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy.update_par_values:1
msgid "快速更新策略的参数值"
msgstr "Quickly update strategy parameter values"

#: of qteasy.strategy.BaseStrategy.update_par_values:3
msgid "策略参数的值，元组中的每个元素是按顺序排列的所有参数值，如果 没有设置参数，则必须传入kwargs参数"
